rComments: Fantastic prof; really nice guy. Cares that students actually learn something, and not just what their grades are. Classes are fun and he's pretty laid-back about homework. Show up and do the work and you'll do fine.

Really nice guy, helpful, makes class fun. I found I didnt learn much in his class though. I didnt really want to go to class after a while. He takes stuff out of the textbook. Tests are easy. Overall a good teacher.
